comments: Fultz (ORL) dislodges Anunoby (TOR) from his rebounding position.
As Banchero (ORL) spins toward the rim, Barnes (TOR) initiates contact with his arm as he starts his upward shooting motion.
Banchero's (ORL) hand slides off Barnes' (TOR) front as he is moving through the pick.
Wagner (ORL) and Barnes (TOR) come together and marginal contact occurs as both players go for the loose ball.

Replay review of the offensive foul called on Trent Jr. (TOR) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful. Wagner (ORL) is set in Trent Jr.'s path and is dislodged from his legal guarding position during Trent Jr.'s driving shot attempt.
VanVleet (TOR) cleanly strips the ball from Wagner (ORL) during his drive towards the rim.
Fultz (ORL) does not beat VanVleet (TOR) to the spot and initiates body contact that affects his SQBR.
VanVleet (TOR) and F. Wagner (ORL) mutually engage and disengage as VanVleet is moving through the pick.
VanVleet (TOR) slightly extends his arm into Wagner (ORL) and the contact during the shot attempt is marginal.
Siakam (TOR) firms up in Fultz's (ORL) path and incidental contact occurs as Fultz is moving through the pick.
Banchero (ORL) moves alongside VanVleet's (TOR) path and maintains a legal guarding position while contesting the shot attempt.
Barnes (TOR) commits a take foul on Banchero (ORL).
